ZH: 我们家住在湖北省。
EN: We live in Hubei Province.

ZH: 他去年去了江苏省出差。
EN: He went on a business trip to Jiangsu Province last year.

ZH: 请你不要浪费水，要节约水源。
EN: Please do not waste water, we need to conserve our water resources.

ZH: 他的爸爸是该省的一名工程师。
EN: His father is an engineer in that province.

ZH: 我们打算去四川省旅行。
EN: We plan to travel to Sichuan Province.

ZH: 这座省会城市有很多古老的建筑。
EN: The provincial capital city has many ancient buildings.

ZH: 我们家的电费省了很多。
EN: Our electricity bill has been significantly reduced.

ZH: 他改变了生活方式，每月都会省下一笔钱。
EN: By changing his lifestyle, he manages to save a significant amount of money each month.

ZH: 这样的整改措施，能够在节省成本的同时提高效率。
EN: These corrective measures can improve efficiency while reducing costs.

ZH: 你把吃剩的食物存起来省到明天再吃。
EN: Save the leftover food for tomorrow.

ZH: 省一点儿能源，对环境也有好处。
EN: Saving energy is beneficial to the environment.

ZH: 如果你不想做饭，可以省事买点外卖。
EN: If you don't feel like cooking, it's convenient to order takeaway.

ZH: 她化了一些妆来省点儿时间。
EN: She put on some makeup to save some time.

ZH: 他不愿意浪费时间在无意义的事情上。
EN: He is not willing to waste time on meaningless things.

ZH: 省下的钱可以用来买新的家具。
EN: The money saved can be used to buy new furniture.

ZH: 这些老房子经过翻新后省了不少钱。
EN: These old houses saved a lot of money after the renovation.

ZH: 她省了时间，但却浪费了很多精力。
EN: She saved time, but wasted a lot of energy.

ZH: 经常锻炼有助于省下看病的钱。
EN: Regular exercise can help save money on medical expenses.

ZH: 他学会了如何有效地省管理财。
EN: He learned how to manage finances effectively and save money.

ZH: 这些绿植居然省了我一点电费。
EN: These plants actually saved me a little on my electricity bill.
